The paper deals with visual recognition and plan recognition, which are both topics in computer vision and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also introduces a new kind of neural network architecture, which falls under the category of machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG a likely sub-category as well. The paper also discusses the use of the proposed model in event recognition tasks, which could fall under robotics (cs.RO) or human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
